imdb.plot outline: A Navy Corpsman accompanies SSGT Seros and SGT Miler on this mission due to an injury SGT Miller sustained en route to their pause. During their time waiting for, one, the Corpsman to finish patching SGT Miller up and two, the arrival of the high value target there are assigned to acquire, the team discusses different scenarios involving celebrities in which they would have to choose from involving fictional circumstances. The game is interrupted by enemy contact and there position is compromise due to an unexpected guest. The team, who is also assisted by a separate fire team, combats the enemy to a position where they can move forward. However, upon request to do so, there are instructed not to advance since a rival sniper team has already acquired the high value target.
